main event: A satellite trail was observed in the sky over Hawaii for 2 minutes.
interesting points: The satellite trail was observed during civil twilight, not at night.
The trail was observed for a longer duration than a typical satellite observation.
The location of the sighting was near Pearl Harbor, Hawaii.
The sighting was reported to the US Air Force, who forwarded the report.
No definite conclusion or intelligence evaluation was provided for the sighting.
